  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">As a Sarutobi, you have inherited the Will of Fire from your forefathers. Beginning at 3rd level, you have found that Focus and Determination is what makes a shinobi strong. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">You gain a number of <em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track)\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track)\">Focus points</strong></em> equal to your proficiency bonus per long rest. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">These Focus Points can be spent to do the following;</span></p><ul><li><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Spend 1 Focus to gain a +2 Bonus on an Attack Roll</span></p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Spend 1 Focus to gain a +2 Bonus on a Saving Throw</span></p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Spend 1 Focus to gain a +2 Bonus on a skill Check</span></p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Spend 3 Focus to gain an Immediate reaction, even with an ability or Jutsu that is an action.</span></p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Spend 3 Focus to automatically Succeed a Death Saving throw.</span></p></li></ul>",
